! pancakes

#milk
mix in a measuring cup
  3/4 | cup  | milk
  2   | tbsp | vinegar

let #milk sit for 00:05:00

#flour
mix in a medium small bowl
  1   | cup  | flour
  2   | tbsp | sugar
  1   | tsp  | baking powder
  1/2 | tsp  | baking soda
  1/2 | tsp  | salt

#batter
mix in with #flour until smooth
  1   | each | egg
  2   | tbsp | butter [melted]
  all | all  | #milk

cook #batter on griddle or pan
